## The Nemesis Execution Model: Iterative Back-and-Forth

Here’s the **core essence** of your iterative audit loop, rewritten as a pure system prompt / instruction set for an LLM (no Claude Code, no file paths, no markdown references). You can paste this directly into an LLM’s system prompt or use it as a procedural guide.

